rows.label: qst702801_msg0001
rows.name:
Prince Adel! What pleasure to see
you again! Is Macmac, most trusted
intelligence operative!

rows.label: qst702801_msg0002
rows.name:
Prince grow so big and gorgeous!
Ahh, if only Macmac was 30 years
younger... Just kidding, of course.

rows.label: qst702801_msg0003
rows.name:
Where was Macmac? Ah yes, case of
poisonous substance dealing. Dumdums
not realize how dangerous that is.

rows.label: qst702801_msg0004
rows.name:
Poisonous substance is Red Pollen
Orb. Some dumdums stupid enough
to buy, and dealer rakes in gold.

rows.label: qst702801_msg0005
rows.name:
Macmac is on trail of dumdums,
but dumdums always seem to be
one step ahead of Macmac.

rows.label: qst702801_msg0006
rows.name:
Which brings Macmac to request.
Prince Adel help efforts of Macmac
to seize Red Pollen Orbs?

rows.label: qst702801_msg0007
rows.name:
Pollen Orb cargo stored in green
barrels. If friends see green barrels,
should smash into pieces on spot!

rows.label: qst702801_msg0008
rows.name:
Under no circumstance use Pollen
Orbs, or Macmac personally show
up and give spankings! Is clear?

rows.label: qst702801_msg0009
rows.name:
Macmac will return to Iira in
meantime and gather more intel
on dumdums.

rows.label: qst702801_msg0010
rows.name:
Will personally expose dumdums
for wrongdoings in name of Prince
Adel!

rows.label: qst702801_msg0011
rows.name:
That about it from side of Macmac.
Please to look for green barrels and
retrieval of Pollen Orbs!
